high_descs: Turn around and head to the sink
Grab the large knife that is on the left of the sink
Cut the potato into slices
Turn around and face the drawers underneath the counter
Open the top left drawer and place the knife inside. Close the drawer
Turn around and head to the sink
Grab one of the slices of potato
Turn to your right and stop at the microwave
Put the potato in the microwave and heat it. Then take the potato out of the microwave.
Turn to your right and stop at the fridge
Open the fridge and place the potato on the second rack
anns.task_desc: Putting a potato slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight and turn to the left to face the sink.
Pick up the small knife from the sink.
Cut the potato on the sink using the knife.
Bring the knife to the cabinet across the sink. Walk to the counter top with a bread knife on top of it.
Put the knife inside the drawer under the counter top with the bread knife on top of it. Close the drawer.
Turn around and walk back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn to the right and face the microwave on the counter top.
Open the microwave, put the slice of potato inside it, close the microwave, heat it for a few seconds, open the microwave, pick up the cooked potato and close the microwave.
Walk to the right to the fridge.
Put the cooked potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the fridge.

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink on the left
grab the knife off of the left side of the kitchen sink
slice the potato up on the left side kitchen sink behind the lettuce
turn around and walk forwards to the kitchen counter, then turn left
place the knife inside the drawer on the left side of the kitchen cabinet on the right
turn left and walk forwards to the kitchen sink
grab a potato slice off of the kitchen sink on the left
turn right and walk to the microwave at the end of the counter on the left
place the potato slice inside of the microwave, microwave it, then take it back out
turn right and walk over to the fridge at the end of the room on the left, turn to face that fridge
place the potato slice inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a cooked potato slice inside of the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the kitchen sink on the left.
Pick up the knife that is next to the cabbage.
Slice the potato located in the back of the cabbage.
Turn around, walk to the counter with the coffee maker and turn left.
Open the top drawer, place the knife inside and and close the drawer.
Return to the kitchen sink.
Take the third slice of potato from the right.
Turn right and walk to the microwave on the left counter.
Open microwave, place potato next to cup, turn on microwave until done, open microwave and remove potato, close microwave door.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the left.
Open fridge door, place potato on shelf with cabbage, close fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a slice of potato and place it in fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk over to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Cut the potato on the left side of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to face the left end of the counter.
Put the knife in the left most drawer under the counter.
Turn left and walk forward to face the left side of the sink.
Pick up a slice of the cut potato.
Turn to the right and walk forward and then face the microwave on the right.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice on the middle shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To cut a potato, heat it, as well as store it in the fridge.
